{"tid":693552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉非禮3名女童　32歲休班警與另一男子被捕","createTime":"2018-06-07T14:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T16:09:43.000Z","uid":81228,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"743d2ab8d6fbb9f7531a9f0f67491bc24b85ebd7","tid":693552,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180607/_2018060722070085087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180607%2F_2018060722070085087.jpg&h=eb8524c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n32歲休班警與另一男子被捕。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n警方接報，指三名女童懷疑在天水圍區被非禮。警方拘捕2名男子，包括一名32歲休班警。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，新界北總區重案組人員接手調查案件，期間發現28歲姓黃男子及32歲姓余休班警務人員分別在網上社交媒體結識3名女童。其後他們各自相約於天水圍區見面，期間女童A（化名）及女童B（化名）懷疑被28歲男子非禮；女童B及女童C（化名）懷疑被32歲休班警非禮。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日分別在屯門區及天水圍區拘捕2名男子，28歲男子涉嫌「非禮」，32歲休班警則涉嫌「非禮」及「向年齡在十六歲以下的兒童作出猥褻行為」。2人已獲准保釋候查，分別須於6月下旬及7月上旬向警方報到。案件由新界北總區重案組第三隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1235580/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1235580%2F&d=Pmc%2BG0prstH3r%2FvXcVSltDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=3c1e5a12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1235580%2F&h=ff34e8bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1235580/</a>"},{"pid":"0c5b32e322ef706fde65b85f066226fd362cbed8","tid":693552,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"休班警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685f876af838dbb9e2b26145cfdfd875bd0c53db","tid":693552,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22599094c7ff91dbf18406b7c99732ec52d91c88","tid":693552,"uid":519